<L>__{exterior grant home night}
<A>__{bill lands hard on the lawn between the two homes. he grabs a .38, and stands beside the window on grant's house. through the window he sees grant barreling down the stairs. bill shoots grant with the .38, shattering the glass. he unloads the clip into him. the diseased townsfolk surround bill, grabbing him. grant, using the others' eyes to see, snaps his tentacle forward, wrapping it around bill's neck, raising him up. grant}
